</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/4876540-jonetta">Jonetta</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I wouldn&apos;t recommend it as part of the pleasure of the series is understanding the nuances of the characters&apos; behaviors. There&apos;s lots of political int<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I wouldn't recommend it as part of the pleasure of the series is understanding the nuances of the characters' behaviors. There's lots of political intrigue that you'd miss by not at least reading the first book. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
