      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="ebook 9781101212011" href="/book/show/9093763-why-mermaids-sing">review of another edition</a>


          <div>
    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Jonetta by: </span>
      <a href="/user/show/4731410-lauren">Lauren</a>
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4876540-jonetta?shelf=historical-mystery">historical-mystery</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4876540-jonetta?shelf=16000-in-2016">16000-in-2016</a>, 
